        "101": {
          "vnum": 101,
          "name": "The Eastern Road",
          "description": "The road bends from the north to the east here, rising steeply along a ridge in the latter direction. A gentle slope to the south leads down to the edge of a wide brown river where it emerges from the woods to the southeast. You can travel north, east, or south.",
