        "102": {
          "vnum": 102,
          "name": "The Eastern Road",
          "description": "Although you stand just below the crest of the hill, the view nevertheless entrances you. Far along the road to the east, you make out the River of Bruenor's Woe as it threads its way out of the mountains and down into the valley to the south. You can head east or west along the road, or south toward the river.",
