          "vnum": 107,
          "name": "Dusty Road",
          "description": "A matted yellow mohawk of grass limply divides the two wide and barren swaths of dirt which make up this road. The road abruptly curves into a pasture and turns into a wide and muddy footpath to the north, and thirstily crawls toward a river to the west.",
