        "108": {
          "vnum": 108,
          "name": "Muddy Path",
          "description": "A road dips into a marshy field here. A nearby river feeds the marsh. Attempts have been made to place rocks in the road to help the traveler, but they are all half-sunken in the mud. The road becomes more dry to the south, and it continues through the tall grass of the field toward the north.",
